25 July 2011Members of the media are invited to a photo opportunity on commencement of the Cabinet Lekgotla tomorrow at the Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria.The photo opportunity will take place as follows:Date: Tuesday, 26 July 2011 Time: 10h30 (Media to be in position by 10h00) Venue: Presidential Guesthouse, PretoriaTo RSVP please email /sms your name, ID number and the media house you represent to: Pheliswa Sebati Cell: 082 413 4609 E-mail: Pheliswa@gcis.gov.za. The deadline for confirmation of attendance is 26 July at 09h00. Kindly note that only media who have confirmed attendance will be given access.Enquiries: Bongiwe Gambu Cell: 082 714 9463Issued by Government Communications (GCIS)